/* About */
"Reticulum Messenger" = "Reticulum Messenger";
"Reticulum Messenger is an open-source iOS client for the Reticulum Network Stack. It uses the LXMF protocol to send and receive encrypted messages over mesh networks, completely independent of traditional internet infrastructure." = "Reticulum Messenger 是一款用于 Reticulum 网络协议栈的开源 iOS 客户端。它使用 LXMF 协议在网状网络上发送和接收加密消息，完全独立于传统互联网基础设施。";
"Reticulum" = "Reticulum";
"Reticulum is a cryptography-based networking protocol designed for unstable and unreliable networks. It provides encrypted, authenticated communication over any medium — from WiFi and cellular to LoRa radio and serial links." = "Reticulum 是一种基于密码学的网络协议，专为不稳定和不可靠的网络设计。它通过任何媒介提供加密、经过认证的通信——从 WiFi 和蜂窝网络到 LoRa 无线电和串行链路。";
"LXMF" = "LXMF";
"LXMF (Lightweight Extensible Message Format) is a messaging protocol built on Reticulum. It supports direct delivery, store-and-forward propagation, and works across any combination of network interfaces." = "LXMF（轻量级可扩展消息格式）是建立在 Reticulum 上的消息传递协议。它支持直接投递、存储转发传播，并可跨任意网络接口组合工作。";
"Privacy" = "隐私";
"All messages are end-to-end encrypted using modern elliptic curve cryptography (X25519 + Ed25519). Your identity exists only on your device — there are no accounts, servers, or phone numbers." = "所有消息均使用现代椭圆曲线密码学（X25519 + Ed25519）进行端到端加密。你的身份仅存在于你的设备上——没有账户、服务器或电话号码。";
"Open Source" = "开源";
"This app is open source under the MIT license. Contributions are welcome! Visit the GitHub repository to get involved." = "本应用在 MIT 许可证下开源。欢迎贡献代码！访问 GitHub 仓库参与其中。";
"Reticulum Network" = "Reticulum 网络";
"LXMF Documentation" = "LXMF 文档";
"Sideband (Android)" = "Sideband（Android）";

